g.title: j1469862827
g.text: This was early 1998

g.title: j3241930566
g.text: But the best lies are the ones you want to believe, ¿verdad?
We had no cure for this disease except a dance with La Flaca
But here he comes
Doktor F and his magical bag of miracles will cure what ails you

g.title: j4058096961
g.text: And we bought it como una bola de mensos
And when the ICR stomps its feet and says "nonono, you cannot help him distribute his drug" should have listened
Vaccines come from scientists not an old man in some ugly-ass trench coat
Selling lies like some old world snake oil
But people are dying all around you?
You help him anyway because you signed up to HELP people

g.title: j8143123
g.text: So we helped him inject the people of this city with his drug
Lined them up in our tents and that cabrón and I shot them full of it one after another
And the others kept the operation safe while we worked

g.title: j597942432

g.title: j1756881841
g.text: I'm not here to tell you what you did can be forgiven or not. That's not something I can do, and honestly - I don't think what you're describing is something that CAN be forgiven.

g.title: j2948312450
g.text: Entrati came here and found exactly what he was looking for - useful, skilled people he could trick into doing what he wanted. Who wouldn't think too hard about it. You fell for his shtick like so many people who came before you.

g.title: j1571832609
g.text: What happened wasn't your fault. You were lied to. Yeah, sure - maybe you were a little willingly blind after things started to go wrong. But who can blame you? Hope is a dangerous drug. And he shot you full of it.

g.title: j2619401078
g.text: People died. People who won't come back. Because you wanted to believe in a miracle drug hawked by some "old man in some ugly-ass trench coat."

g.title: j2455991200
g.text: You wanted to believe his lies. And so you did. And that's on you. And all the people who got sick because of it? That's also on you.

g.title: j638622045
g.text: So of course, you went along with it. Of course, you wanted to believe there was a chance.

g.title: j2703113057

g.title: j2300875561

g.title: j532412179
